---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="赞助支持" description="感谢您的支持">
  <div class="donate-page">
    <h1>赞助支持</h1>
    <p>如果您觉得我的内容对您有帮助，欢迎通过微信赞赏码进行赞助支持。</p>
    
    <div class="donate-content">
      <div class="qr-code-section">
        <h2>微信赞赏码</h2>
        <img src="/wx.jpg" alt="微信赞赏码" class="qr-code" />
        <p>扫描上方二维码，通过微信进行赞助</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="donate-message">
        <h3>感谢您的支持</h3>
        <p>您的赞助将帮助我持续创作优质内容，感谢您的鼓励与支持！</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .donate-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  
  .donate-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .qr-code-section {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .qr-code {
    max-width: 300px;
    height: auto;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  
  .donate-message {
    text-align: center;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
  }
  
  h1, h2, h3 {
    color: #333;
  }
  
  p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>